T1  - FW/SM: A Prototype Structured Modeling Environment
AU  - Geoffrion, Arthur M.
Y1  - 1991/12/01
PY  - 1991
DA  - 1991/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.37.12.1513
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.37.12.1513
T2  - Management Science
JF  - Management Science
JO  - Management Science
SP  - 1513
EP  - 1538
VL  - 37
IS  - 12
PB  - INFORMS
N2  - A research prototype implementation has been evolving for several years in parallel with the vision, theory, language, and applicative aspects of structured modeling. The objective of this article is to describe the capabilities of this implementation as it now stands, and to comment on how it contributes toward fulfilling a previously published agenda for the development of a new generation of modeling environments. The intended audience is all modeling system designers and evaluators, including those who do not happen to take a structured modeling approach.
